{"tid":2098251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當局稱學校若有確診須停課　全港停課要考慮一籃子因素","createTime":"2020-07-07T10:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T14:26:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d5785d91e0257dc4ac551d5c15fc650e35c4f059","tid":2098251,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"今日確診的患者當中，部分與學校相關，例如患者屬學生，涉及學校包括中華基督教會扶輪中學、東華三院馮黃鳳亭中學及崇真小學。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君說，如果校內有人感染新型肺炎，有關學校必須先停課14天。<br />\n<br />\n至於是否需要全港停課，她表示，需由政府考慮一籃子因素，再作決定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536359-20200707.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536359-20200707.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=de54fcb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536359-20200707.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5f74935d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536359-20200707.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c7175f4143244a48446a27c73674e2146be4f35e","tid":2098251,"uid":39268,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:19:14.000Z","msg":"一籃子？匪語？"},{"pid":"2c1b31acfa37aabc7bba586a3b39e8fd21f1fe9b","tid":2098251,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7175f4143244a48446a27c73674e2146be4f35e","tid":2098251,"uid":39268,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:19:14.000Z","msg":"一籃子？匪語？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:20:17.000Z","msg":"一男子689"},{"pid":"527b9b977618ade0563f064ed4e2e30362a0fb6e","tid":2098251,"uid":33143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"gchi唔好停<br />\n比佢繼續爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06923590ae12fb2fa7cf4335429d036ced97708d","tid":2098251,"uid":101307,"like":0,"d